Design a modern mobile-first product detail page for a natural food e-commerce app.

Style:
- Clean, minimal, premium UI
- Soft pastel background (light beige / off-white)
- Organic/eco-friendly design
- Rounded corners, soft shadows
- Elegant typography (serif for headings, sans-serif for body)

Layout:

1. Product Title Section:
- Show product name in local language (Telugu) + English translation
- Example:
  "చింతకాయ పచ్చడి (Chintakaya Pachadi)"
- Subtitle description:
  "Tangy traditional raw tamarind pickle made with fresh green tamarind and spices."

2. Key Benefits Section:
- Title: "Key Benefits:"
- Bullet points:
  - Rich in Vitamin C
  - Aids Digestion
  - Traditional Recipe
- Use small colored dot icons (yellow/gold)

3. Size Selection:
- Title: "Select Size"
- Show 3 options:
  - 250g ₹100 (selected state highlighted with border + glow)
  - 500g ₹200
  - 1kg ₹400
- Rounded pill-style buttons
- Selected option should have colored border (gold/green)

4. Quantity Selector:
- Title: "Quantity"
- Horizontal stepper:
  [-]   1   [+]
- Rounded container with soft background
- Buttons should be elevated (shadow)

5. Add to Cart Button:
- Full width button
- Rounded (pill shape)
- Text: "+ Add to Cart"
- Soft shadow
- Subtle hover/press animation

6. UI Behavior:
- When size changes → update price
- Quantity stepper updates total
- Add to cart triggers toast notification

Design Requirements:
- Mobile-first layout
- Spacing: generous padding
- Use subtle animations
- Premium feel like a modern organic brand
- No clutter, focus on usability

Color Palette:
- Primary: Green / Olive
- Accent: Gold / Yellow
- Background: Soft cream

Extras:
- Smooth transitions
- Touch-friendly UI
- Clean alignment


Build a responsive React + Tailwind product detail page.

Features:
- Dynamic size selection (updates price)
- Quantity increment/decrement
- Add to Cart functionality
- State management using useState

UI:
- Telugu + English product title
- Benefits list
- Size selector buttons
- Quantity stepper
- Add to cart button

Logic:
- Default size selected (250g)
- Price updates based on selected size
- Quantity cannot go below 1
- Add to cart stores product in cart state

UX:
- Highlight selected size
- Button animations
- Toast message on add to cart

Design:
- Clean, minimal, eco-friendly
- Rounded UI
- Soft shadows
- Mobile-first
